00:28.959 --> 00:33.521
Detective Sipowicz, please tell the court
how you came to arrest Mr. Giardella.

00:33.597 --> 00:36.088
This past August 27 th,

00:36.166 --> 00:40.262
I was routinely surveilling the
defendant because he's a known felon.

00:40.337 --> 00:44.239
During the course of the surveillance,
I observed the defendant's vehicle...

00:44.308 --> 00:48.301
have a flat tire, and he got out of
the Cadillac and he opened the trunk.

00:48.379 --> 00:52.440
At that time I approached the vehicle,
identified myself as a police officer,

00:52.516 --> 00:55.883
and in the course of casual observation
of the open trunk,

00:55.953 --> 01:00.913
I saw 27 cartons of filter cigarettes
which did not have tax stamps.

01:00.991 --> 01:04.927
I ascertained that the vehicle
was owned by the defendant.

01:04.995 --> 01:07.293
I gave him his rights
and took him into custody.

01:07.364 --> 01:09.730
Nothing further, Your Honor.

01:09.800 --> 01:11.734
Detective Sipowicz,

01:14.605 --> 01:18.006
you've testified that the cartons
of untaxed cigarettes,

01:18.075 --> 01:21.306
for possession of which you arrested
Mr. Giardella, were in plain sight...

01:21.378 --> 01:25.075
in Mr. Giardella's trunk when he opened
it to get out a jack to fix the flat.

01:25.149 --> 01:29.586
- Right.
- Now, there were seven nails...

01:29.653 --> 01:32.816
in Mr. Giardella's
right rear radial, Detective.

01:32.890 --> 01:36.087
That wouldn't exactly
produce a slow leak.

01:36.160 --> 01:39.596
Yet you say that during several hours
of antecedent surveillance...

01:39.663 --> 01:43.690
you saw no one damage
Mr. Giardella's tire.

01:43.767 --> 01:47.703
I was surveilling Mr. Giardella,
not his car, Counselor.

01:47.771 --> 01:50.103
He stopped at
Niglio's Coffee House.

01:50.174 --> 01:52.267
Maybe, uh...
Maybe some urban youths...

01:52.343 --> 01:56.109
- did mischief to his vehicle
during that time frame.

01:56.180 --> 02:00.116
Your Honor, uh, justified or not,

02:00.184 --> 02:04.245
the reputation of the neighborhood in
which Niglio's Coffee House is located...

02:04.321 --> 02:06.687
is such that urban youths"...

02:06.757 --> 02:10.658
do not tend to congregate
and do mischief in its environs.

02:10.728 --> 02:13.993
Maybe he drove past a construction site
after he left the place.

02:14.064 --> 02:18.160
Detective Sipowicz is known to have a
personal vendetta against Mr. Giardella.

02:18.235 --> 02:22.865
I submit that the true scenario is that
while my client stopped at Niglio's,

02:22.940 --> 02:27.206
Detective Sipowicz hammered nails
into his tire and caused a flat,

02:27.277 --> 02:31.338
so that when Mr. Giardella
stopped to get out a spare,

02:31.415 --> 02:34.748
the detective could circumvent
probable cause statutes...

02:34.818 --> 02:39.050
and go fishing inside
Mr. Giardella's trunk.

02:39.123 --> 02:43.753
Move to suppress the evidence as tainted
and dismiss the complaint.

02:43.827 --> 02:45.761
Granted.

02:45.829 --> 02:48.662
- What about the construction-site
theory? - Pathetic.

02:48.732 --> 02:50.927
Adjourned.

02:51.001 --> 02:53.333
Hey, what is that,
a dead rat you got on your head?

02:53.404 --> 02:55.497
Now make some bad-wig jokes.

02:55.572 --> 02:58.234
Meanwhile, I'm walking out the door,
you nickel stiff.

02:58.308 --> 03:02.472
Sipowicz, what is it you clear, about 90 a
day? Here, go buy yourself some clean socks.

03:02.546 --> 03:06.277
I'm gonna burn you down, you
small-time operator. You count on it.

03:06.350 --> 03:09.217
- Let's lay off him. - No shot. That
wig-wearing hump rubs me the wrong way.

03:09.286 --> 03:11.379
I'm gonna make his life miserable.

03:11.455 --> 03:14.083
- And bury your own career in the bargain.
- Who are you kiddin', John?

03:14.158 --> 03:17.389
- They already held that service.
- Andy...

03:17.461 --> 03:21.921
Hey, Miss District Attorney. You really
prosecuted the crap outta that one.

03:21.999 --> 03:24.194
