special attention on an apartment building?

15:12.118 --> 15:15.645
- Give me the address. I'll take care of it.
- Got a piece of paper?

15:15.722 --> 15:18.885
- Right.
- This is my wi...

15:18.959 --> 15:21.359
uh, ex-wife's address.

15:21.428 --> 15:25.865
